title: Fly like a bird 3 v1.5 [PD]
description:
Have you ever dreamed of flying like a bird? Well ,here's your chance, and more.
Fly about, forage for food, build nests, raise chicks, and wait for it... Poo on people!

This web cult classic from gamevial finally arrives on the android with all the features and birds that you know and love, including four seperate landscapes, MMO or Multi-player and single player mode.

What's New:

Beta 2.853 Big update, new landscape, industry
IMPORTANT:
Quality is now much higher, please lower resolution and quality in "options" if it plays too slow on your device.
(It still should look much better than it did in previous versions :) )
Macaw and Ringnecked parakeet added
bug fixes
